    <published>2023-06-29T06:26:52.503Z</published>
    <updated>2023-09-14T03:52:06.433Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="如何让顶部图和下面连起来"><a href="#如何让顶部图和下面连起来" class="headerlink" title="如何让顶部图和下面连起来"></a><font color=CadetBlue >如何让顶部图和下面连起来</font></h2><ul><li><font color=LightSeaGreen size=3>主题下的_config.yml文件找到 <font color=Red>index_img: transparent</font></font></li><li><font color=CadetBlue size=3>在自己的css文件中添加：</font><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_">#</span><span class="language-bash">page-header:not(.not-top-img):before &#123;</span></span><br><span class="line">    background-color: transparent !important;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_">#</span><span class="language-bash">page-header.post-bg:before &#123;</span></span><br><span class="line">    position: absolute;</span><br><span class="line">    top: 0;</span><br><span class="line">    left: 0;</span><br><span class="line">    display: block;</span><br><span class="line">    width: 100%;</span><br><span class="line">    height: 100%;</span><br><span class="line">    background-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.5) !important;</span><br><span class="line">    content: &#x27;&#x27;;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul>]]></content>
    
    
